World's first human CI/CD

Increment version:
iso8583.__init__.__version__

Update change log:
CHANGELOG.rst

Doctest:
python -m doctest .\iso8583\__init__.py
python -m doctest .\iso8583\encoder.py
python -m doctest .\iso8583\decoder.py
python -m doctest .\iso8583\tools.py

Lint:
black iso8583
black tests
flake8 --max-line-length 80 --select B950 --extend-ignore E203, E501

Unit test:
pytest

Coverage:
pytest --cov=./iso8583 .
coverage html
coverage xml
codecov -f coverage.xml -t <token>

Docs:
python -m readme_renderer .\README.rst
.\docs\make.bat html

Build:
python .\setup.py sdist bdist_wheel

Upload to test:
python -m twine upload --repository-url https://test.pypi.org/legacy/ dist/*

Upload to production:
python -m twine upload dist/*
